<a href="../../../tools/emf/scripts/sdo.php" label="Service Data Object (SDO)" id="Service Data Object (SDO)">Service Data Objects</a> (<a href="../../../tools/emf/scripts/sdo.php" label="Service Data Object (SDO)" id="Service Data Object (SDO)">SDO</a>) is a framework that simplifies and unifies data application development in a service oriented architecture (SOA). It supports and integrates XML and incorporates J2EE patterns and best practices. EMF includes an EMF-based implementation of <a href="../../../tools/emf/scripts/sdo.php" label="Service Data Object (SDO)" id="Service Data Object (SDO)">Service Data Objects</a> (<a href="../../../tools/emf/scripts/sdo.php" label="Service Data Object (SDO)" id="Service Data Object (SDO)">SDO</a>). 

